.Sh NAME
.Nm rpirtc
.Nd Raspberry Pi real-time clock
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "rpirtc* at fdt?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the firmware-managed real-time clock found
in the Raspberry Pi 5.
